{"tid":270874,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 我個fd 番左大陸讀d 咩領導課程","createTime":"2017-06-04T15:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T15:55:38.000Z","uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15285a6406a9997a8704bf9ce7a429225690ccb6","tid":270874,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:19:13.000Z","msg":"我個fd 番左大陸讀d 咩領導課程<br />\n<br />\n未上去讀之前話咩係教心理既野，<br />\n<br />\n點知比我地發現讀d 野完全同心理冇關係<br />\n<br />\n個課程每星期畢業一次，讀一個月<br />\n<br />\n依家佢讀完好似比人洗左腦咁，<br />\n<br />\n係咁sell 周圍d fd 番大陸讀，<br />\n<br />\n仲喊晒口求d fd 讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成班fd 都好擔心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以教下點救番佢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20dda8845e7ae0a3bec19569b8a339801c77ff9","tid":270874,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:19:51.000Z","msg":"傳銷，冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bddb7c66ac1a2f7de7eb4d318898058ba28921","tid":270874,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"你要交代下佢背景先<br />\n<br />\n先可以對症下藥。<br />\n<br />\n佢本身性格點<br />\n<br />\n有咩成為佢為啦啦走去掂呢d野既導火線<br />\n<br />\n佢同屋企人朋友關係點<br />\n<br />\n有邊個勸佢佢多數會聽<br />\n（邊個對佢最大影響力）<br />\n<br />\n有冇借錢讀課程<br />\n<br />\n有冇職都辭埋玩自閉，淨係同課程班人玩<br />\n<br />\netc"},{"pid":"d81f81b631e76e47662df1e94fa68eeab229cdfe","tid":270874,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:23:47.000Z","msg":"同埋佢幾多歲<br />\n<br />\n我估佢係男啦<br />\n<br />\n幾十歲果d無得救<br />\n固執仲要自作聰明<br />\n<br />\n十幾二十可能只需要人更多的關心。。。"},{"pid":"4c2f332d164ea3233b9ff257af68253217e74c48","tid":270874,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"人蠢冇藥醫架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e49a8b7103eef6660eb121fc3dcf913209e062","tid":270874,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要交代下佢背景先<br />\n<br />\n先可以對症下藥。<br />\n<br />\n佢本身性格點<br />\n<br />\n有咩成為佢為啦啦走去掂呢d野既導火線<br />\n<br />\n佢同屋企人朋友關係點<br />\n<br />\n有邊個勸佢佢多數會聽<br />\n（邊個對佢最大影響力）<br />\n<br />\n有冇借錢讀課程<br />\n<br />\n有冇職都辭埋玩自閉，淨係同課程班人玩<br />\n<br />\netc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢做裝修的<br />\n<br />\n之前成個月日日都開工<br />\n<br />\n之後就成個月唔做野上左大陸讀<br />\n<br />\n依家真係玩自閉<br />\n因為平時我地成班fd 會打下波，<br />\n佢依家打都唔打<br />\n<br />\n有幾個最好既fd都勸佢叫佢唔好讀，<br />\n但佢都冇聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n性格：太好人，但心事會收收埋埋個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 佢打晒比全部fd 都冇打比我，可能就到我<br />\n我應該講d 咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05d7b41e9f0ab18d7a98716e210fecee268151b","tid":270874,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋佢幾多歲<br />\n<br />\n我估佢係男啦<br />\n<br />\n幾十歲果d無得救<br />\n固執仲要自作聰明<br />\n<br />\n十幾二十可能只需要人更多的關心。。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n男<br />\n<br />\n應該27歲<br />\n<br />\n佢好鐘意鬥氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}